# Docs first

Project source of truth lives in `docs/`. Before implementing or changing product behavior, UI, or architecture:

1. Read the relevant file(s) under `docs/` (start with `docs/PRD.md` for product scope)
2. Follow what those docs specify — do not invent conflicting product rules
3. If docs and code disagree, ask clarification before implementing and flag the mismatch
4. For UI, also follow the Design rule (`docs/design/DESIGN.md`, `@bulaa/design`)
